de.mpa.algorithms.fragmentation

Class Fragmentizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mpa.algorithms.fragmentation.Fragmentizer

  • public class Fragmentizer
extends Object
    This class is used to do a calculation for the theoretical masses of a, b, c, x, y and z ions (plus double charged ones) and do the matching of experimental and theoretical masses.
    Author:
    Thilo Muth
